{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"13a3729a8f","title":"在全国第二批城市“四清”部署情况简报上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1fa9c2a9d7","index":0,"year":1965,"month":10,"day":30,"articleId":"13a3729a8f"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"db7ed8c549","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"13a3729a8f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央办公厅1965年10月30日编印的《情况简报》第三六五号上。简报说：一、据不完全统计，全国27个省、市、自治区（不包括西藏）第二批开展城市“四清”运动的单位共有16100多个，职工6955000余人，占全国职工总数的30%左右。二、参加第二批城市“四清”运动的工作队共计282000多人。新老队员的比例，有的地区老队员占40%至50%，有的地区只占20%左右。工作队员与参加运动职工人数的比例，据两个大区的统计，中南为1：20，东北为1：26。简报还附有部分中央局和省、市、区党委负责同志薄点名单。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0aea6341ed","type":"title","text":"在全国第二批城市“四清”部署情况简报上的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"13a3729a8f"},{"id":"db7ed8c549","type":"paragraph","text":"江青阅。大有希望，明冬后春可完","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"13a3729a8f"},{"id":"99ba2fa60d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"13a3729a8f"},{"id":"68ffa07b28","type":"paragraph","text":"开日上午五时","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"13a3729a8f"}],"page":{"id":"3d9f482724","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"13a3729a8f","start":230,"end":230}}}},"__N_SSG":true}